
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Someone who looks after the child when he fell asleep<br />
Someone who puts a million stars in the infinity<br />
Someone who will always guide the swallows to faraway lands<br />
Someone who shows to the desperate the way that will save him</p>
<p>That something marvellous that lighted my life<br />
With a wonderful sun &#8211; the tenderness of your love<br />
You, only you, are a ray of light in my life<br />
You, joy, calm and peace spring</p>
